extends emailBase 

block content 
    p Hi #{name},
        p Welcome to Natours, we're so glad to have you! 🎉🙏
        p We're all a big family here, so if there is anything we can do to make you feel at home, please do not hesitate to let us know. 
        p To get started, please make sure to upload a user photo so we can identify you a little easier for when you book your first tour!
        table.btn.btn-primary(role='presentation', border='0', cellpadding='0', cellspacing='0')
            tbody
                tr
                    td(align='left')
                        table(role='presentation', border='0', cellpadding='0', cellspacing='0')
                            tbody
                                tr
                                    td
                                        a(href=`${linkUrl}`, target='_blank') Upload user photo
        p If you need any assistance booking your first tour, you may reach out to one of our customer support representatives, and they will be happy to support you!
        p - #{from}, CEO